  "texts": [
    "For the labels \"cardiomegaly,\" \"consolidation,\" \"edema,\" and \"pleural effusion,\" we recorded the average score across multiple datasets to facilitate a comprehensive performance comparison of the model on these four critical labels.",
    "Gemini-Pro-Vision was excluded from the analysis for \"pneumothorax\" due to the absence of positive samples, which is indicated as N/A in the tableThe model achieved an overall average F1 score of 0.56, excelling particularly in the detection of cardiomegaly (0.62), edema (0.67), and pneumonia (0.63).",
    "However, its performance in detecting pneumothorax was notably lower (0.05) providing finer details.",
    "These factors could contribute to the model's suboptimal performance in detecting subtle lesions.",
    "Third, the model intentionally omits descriptions of supporting devices such as feeding tubes and endotracheal tubes in CXRs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}